  git://github.com/OpenImageIO/oiio.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack OpenImageIO-1.1.7-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./OpenImageIO-1.1.7-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/OpenImageIO-1.1.7-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/OpenImageIO-1.1.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOpenImageIO1.1-1.1.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libOpenImageIO-devel-1.1.7-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/python-OpenImageIO-1.1.7-X.tar.bz2

